import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import "./ResumeTemplate.css"; // Import a CSS file if you want to move the styles const ResumeTemplate = () => { const [resumeData, setResumeData] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { axios .get("https://your-api-url.com/resume-data") // Replace with your API URL .then((response) => { setResumeData(response.data); }) .catch((error) => { console.error(error); }); }, []); return (
Resume
{resumeData.name}
Mobile : {resumeData.mobile}
Email : {resumeData.email}
Address :{" "} {resumeData.address}
Objective {resumeData.objective}
Experience {resumeData.experiences && resumeData.experiences.map((experience, index) => (
- {experience.jobRole}{" "} ({experience.duration} )
{experience.company}
{experience.workingFrom} {" "} â€“{" "} {experience.workingTo}
{experience.workDescription}
))}
Education {resumeData.education && resumeData.education.map((education, index) => (
- {education.course}
{education.institute}
{education.date}
))}
Skills {resumeData.skills && resumeData.skills.map((skill, index) => (
- {skill}
))}
Personal Details
Date of Birth :{" "} {resumeData.personalDetails && resumeData.personalDetails.dob}
Gender :{" "} {resumeData.personalDetails && resumeData.personalDetails.gender}
Religion :{" "} {resumeData.personalDetails && resumeData.personalDetails.religion}
Nationality :{" "} {resumeData.personalDetails && resumeData.personalDetails.nationality}
); }; export default ResumeTemplate;
